Function is a block of code used to perform some specific task 

Types:- 

1.Built in function:- standard function  

Eg:- 

Print(),input(),type(),help(),dir() etc 

  builtins module 

    User defined function:- 

     We can create our own function 

Advantage: 

1.code readability 

2.code reusability 

 

syntax:- 

By using def keyword function in python 

def  function_name(arguments) : 

       Block of code 

function_name(values) 

 

Types of argument: 

    default argument:- 

    Keyword argument:- 

    Positional argument 

    arbitrary argument:- 

 

1.default argument:- 

default argument is a parameter that assume default value if value is not provided by caller. 

 

def fun(name,age): 

      Print(name=10 

                Age='xyz') 

fun(10,'xyz') 

Keyword argument:- 

Are passing value with respect to name. if the position change also value will not change. 

Fun definition will receive like dict. 

 

